-- Gazprom’s Partner in Northgas Selling 49% Stake, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2012-08-21T04:03:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/gazprom-s-partner-in-northgas-selling-49-stake-vedomosti-says.html
Farkhad Akhmedov, OAO Gazprom’s
partner in ZAO Northgas, exercised a put option to sell his 49
percent stake in the venture to Gazprom, Vedomosti reported,
citing Akhmedov.  The price could vary from $1.8 billion to $2.6 billion and
the transaction may be completed in November or December, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Arkhipov in Moscow at 
 iarkhipov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
